title: A Stranger in Town (1943; smallest download)

sources.title: A Stranger In Town
sources.description: Actors: Frank Morgan ("The Wizard of Oz"); Richard Carlson; Jean Rogers; Olin Howland; Chill Wills; Porter Hall; John Hodiak Runtime: 1:06:50 Vacationing incognito in a small town, a supreme court justice discovers rampant corruption and abuse of governmental powers. This is in the public domain because the copyright wasn't renewed after 28 years.
